      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a mechanically sound example of the S54-powered legend. The 3.2L naturally aspirated straight-six features a 8,000 RPM redline, individual throttle bodies, and a recently serviced double-VANOS system. Power is managed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates, and the suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein dampers and poly-bushes for sharpened turn-in and reduced lateral deflection. While the paint shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the engine pulls cleanly through the rev range with no VANOS rattle or subframe cracks. A true driver\u2019s spec with the essential 'Big Three' maintenance items addressed.",
